OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome low
OL,6,Fcloud covers the north coast of
OL,7,FCornwall. Otherwise a clear night to
OL,8,Fcome with light winds. Mist and fog
OL,9,Fdeveloping in prone spots in the
OL,10,Fsouthwest. Feeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny mist and fog will lift
OL,13,Fquickly, leaving a bright and sunny
OL,14,Fday for all. Feeling hot in the strong
OL,15,Fsunshine, especially in the east.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FRemaining dry with plenty of strong
OL,19,FJuly sunshine. Feeling hot by day with
OL,20,Fnights also turning increasingly warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
